{"tid":1555951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線既世界","createTime":"2019-09-09T14:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:23:33.000Z","uid":313039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a49f28714984193933ffe79a774f231ee3fe8eb","tid":1555951,"uid":313039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"望住咁多位手足咁努力<br />\n我真係好多謝自己生於呢個香港。<br />\n<br />\n但望住一日一日既發展<br />\n同時間有好多手足受傷 被捕<br />\n個心好痛好痛<br />\n<br />\n呢一種無力感無限放大<br />\n好驚個結果唔知會係點<br />\n<br />\n已經頹到無覆whatsapp 連Ig都del 埋<br />\n想靜下個人發覺 愈諗愈多 一睇連登就喊...<br />\n<br />\n對唔住大家 我唔係有心講呢啲說話<br />\n但我真係就快頂唔住<br />\n好希望大家支持落去 <br />\n<br />\n「同行兒女 為正義 時代革命」<br />\n好希望大家不忘初衷 為正義 光復香港。"},{"pid":"ff5787c9092489119e5cf779ca565dcf38b784a7","tid":1555951,"uid":313039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"對唔住大家 唔係有心放負"},{"pid":"afc875f4589a89aca8adf6e96ff54064750108c0","tid":1555951,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fn0Etm6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFn0Etm6.jpg&h=baca4433&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c526d296caeea2d0aed0faf79abf6032747fa68","tid":1555951,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"我老豆中出過蘿飯焦雞<br />\n已fact checked<br />\nconfirm 咗<br />\n冇套<br />\n佢最鐘意d老雞 好撚重口味 滴蠟都玩齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9cb6128fc9748763973168d647aeefd1f3b90b","ti